AppSocially,is,a,service,for,making,applications,engaging,and,viral,AppSocially,helps,application,developers,and,companies,engage,with,their,users,and,understand,their,needs,and,wants,The,AppSocially,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,AppSocially,with,other,applications,The,API,allows,for,metric,and,data,tracking,of,user,activity,and,application,virality